{"tid":1465811,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共喉舌《環球時報》記者機場遭圍毆","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:34:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3016b3c7dd157eae5a9cb0a9419429acfc6094","tid":1465811,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"一名中年男子被指假冒記者，被抗爭者用索帶鎖起雙手，並被搜出持有一本付姓男子的內地護照、一張雙程證和一名香港警察的卡片。他接受《蘋果》直播訪問時，對鏡頭舉起V字手勢。《蘋果》在網上搜尋該男子的姓名，發現其名字與中共喉舌《環球時報》記者相符。<br />\n<br />\n該名《環時》記者日前在「全民撐警日」，報道「香港各界愛國愛港人士」發起的撐警活動。其中一張觀塘警署拍攝的照片，註明為「環球時報 - 環球網赴香港特派記者付國豪」拍攝。該報道亦有提及中區警署的撐警活動，但相片未有註明攝影者。"},{"pid":"6fac59eca64c05e631054670713c978cb7a212ad","tid":1465811,"uid":47857,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056503a508b7ab7713dc87845d6da355daaa5d91","tid":1465811,"uid":281966,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">熱烈地彈琴 熱烈地唱</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1b6596ba919d07b53bf79a00632f2fe1f682be","tid":1465811,"uid":178459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"反中共 反獨裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427d54335d07525b3a4100f5508ac5514d8bcc8a","tid":1465811,"uid":291321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"大陸記者全部都是國安"},{"pid":"1d202b4f00efac5bb14193d2fc15f48c189f69b7","tid":1465811,"uid":32716,"like":2,"dislike":